name: Gonawi
description:
The Alien Frog Force has deployed 50 elite units to the Earth. Their mission is to make our beloved planet inhospitable for humans and pave the way for the alien invasion. 

It is now up to you and your old friends Smith & Wesson to stop them. But be careful, you cannot let a single one of these elite frogs slip by or the world will surely come to an end faster than you can say wait what are these blue frogs wearing some kind of black vest or something?
